[
    {
        "text": "You’d probably never notice a tiny \njumping spider in your living room,",
        "start": 0.22,
        "duration": 3.34
    },
    {
        "text": "but it’d surely notice you.",
        "start": 3.56,
        "duration": 2.699
    },
    {
        "text": "While the arachnids are famous",
        "start": 6.259,
        "duration": 1.28
    },
    {
        "text": "for their excellent vision\nand vibration detection,",
        "start": 7.539,
        "duration": 2.72
    },
    {
        "text": "new research shows that despite\ntheir lack of ear drums,",
        "start": 10.26,
        "duration": 2.48
    },
    {
        "text": "they can also hear sounds.",
        "start": 12.74,
        "duration": 2.5
    },
    {
        "text": "Researchers discovered this\nby putting tiny electrodes",
        "start": 15.24,
        "duration": 2.68
    },
    {
        "text": "in the sound-sensitive parts\nof the spiders’ brains",
        "start": 17.92,
        "duration": 2.439
    },
    {
        "text": "and placing them on a metal box",
        "start": 20.359,
        "duration": 1.76
    },
    {
        "text": "that cancelled out\nvibrations from below.",
        "start": 22.119,
        "duration": 2.74
    },
    {
        "text": "Then they played a sound at the\nsame frequency as the buzz of a wasp",
        "start": 24.859,
        "duration": 3.32
    },
    {
        "text": "that preys upon jumping spiders.",
        "start": 28.18,
        "duration": 2.24
    },
    {
        "text": "Not only did the spiders\nfreeze and look around",
        "start": 30.429,
        "duration": 2.48
    },
    {
        "text": "just as they’d do when\nstartled in the wild,",
        "start": 32.909,
        "duration": 2.56
    },
    {
        "text": "but data from the electrode\nshowed brain activity",
        "start": 35.47,
        "duration": 2.32
    },
    {
        "text": "spiked in the auditory area, too.",
        "start": 37.79,
        "duration": 2.61
    },
    {
        "text": "This shows they actually hear sounds,",
        "start": 40.4,
        "duration": 2.24
    },
    {
        "text": "from a wasp dive-bombing",
        "start": 42.64,
        "duration": 2.16
    },
    {
        "text": "to you crunching a potato chip.",
        "start": 44.8,
        "duration": 3.1
    }
]